'''二硒化锗'''是一种[[无机化合物|无机化合物]]，化学式为GeSe<sub>2</sub>。它可由[[锗|锗]]和[[硒|硒]]按化学计量比反应，或[[硒化氢|硒化氢]]和[[四氯化锗|四氯化锗]]反应得到：<ref name=Iva />
:<math>\mathsf{Ge + 2Se \ \xrightarrow \ GeSe_2 }</math>
:<math>\mathsf{GeCl_4 + 2H_2Se \ \xrightarrow \ GeSe_2 + 4HCl }</math>

它和[[硒|硒]]、[[联氨|联氨]]反应，可以得到黄色的(N<sub>2</sub>H<sub>5</sub>)<sub>4</sub>Ge<sub>2</sub>Se<sub>6</sub>。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Inorganic Chemistry|volume=44|issue=10|language=en|issn=0020-1669|date=2005-05|pages=3755–3761|doi=10.1021/ic048276l|url=https://pubs.acs.org/doi/10.1021/ic048276l|title=Synthesis, Structure, and Thermal Properties of Soluble Hydrazinium Germanium(IV) and Tin(IV) Selenide Salts|accessdate=2021-01-23|author=David B. Mitzi}}</ref>
:<math>\mathsf{2GeSe_2 + 2Se + 5N_2H_4 \ \xrightarrow \ (N_2H_5)_4Ge_2Se_6 + N_2 }</math>
它和[[硒化铅|硒化铅]]、[[硒化镓|硒化镓]]<!-- Ga2Se3 -->在高温反应，可以得到PbGa<sub>2</sub>GeSe<sub>6</sub>。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Crystal Growth & Design|volume=19|issue=8|language=en|issn=1528-7483|date=2019-08-07|pages=4224–4228|doi=10.1021/acs.cgd.9b00118|url=https://pubs.acs.org/doi/10.1021/acs.cgd.9b00118|title=Crystal Growth and Characterization of a New Quaternary Chalcogenide Nonlinear Crystal for the Mid-Infrared: PbGa 2 GeSe 6|accessdate=2021-01-23|author=Valeriy V. Badikov, Dmitrii V. Badikov, Li Wang, Galina S. Shevyrdyaeva, Vladimir L. Panyutin, Anna A. Fintisova, Svetlana G. Sheina, Valentin Petrov|archive-date=2021-07-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210726055538/https://pubs.acs.org/doi/10.1021/acs.cgd.9b00118}}</ref>

